<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset="utf-8" /><meta content="IE=edge,chrome=1" http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" /><title>Lift: Form fields attributes</title><link href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Droid+Sans:400,700|Bitter:400,700,400italic|Open+Sans:300italic,400italic,700italic,400,300,700" media="screen" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" /><link href="../assets/stylesheets/all-f5ec2720.css" media="screen" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" /><script src="../assets/javascripts/all-eca7008a.js" type="text/javascript"></script></head><body class="x2010 x2010_lift-form-fields-attributes"><div class="navbar navbar-default"><div class="navbar-collapse collapse navbar-responsive-collapse"><div class="container"><ul class="nav navbar-nav"><li><a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Blog</a></li><li><a class="navbar-brand" href="/about.html">About</a></li><li><a class="navbar-brand" href="/projects.html">Projects</a></li><li><a class="navbar-brand" href="/talks.html">Talks</a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="container"><article class="post"><div class="page-header"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-10"><h1>Lift: Form fields attributes</h1></div><div class="col-md-2 post-date"><time datetime="2010-02-17">Feb 17, 2010</time></div></div></div><div class="alert alert-info">This article was originally
<a href="http://tumblr.teamon.eu/post/395033779/lift-form-fields-attributes">published at Tumblr</a>.</div><div class="lead"><pre class="highlight scala"><span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">Sample</span> <span class="o">{</span>
  <span class="k">def</span> <span class="n">sample</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">xhtml</span><span class="k">:</span> <span class="kt">NodeSeq</span><span class="o">)</span><span class="k">:</span> <span class="kt">NodeSeq</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="o">{</span>
    <span class="n">bind</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="s">"f"</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">xhtml</span><span class="o">,</span>
      <span class="s">"one"</span> <span class="o">-&gt;</span> <span class="nc">SHtml</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">text</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="s">""</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">e</span> <span class="k">=&gt;</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="o">),</span>
      <span class="s">"two"</span> <span class="o">-&gt;</span> <span class="nc">SHtml</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">text</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="s">""</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">e</span> <span class="k">=&gt;</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="o">),</span>
      <span class="s">"three"</span> <span class="o">-%&gt;</span> <span class="nc">SHtml</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">text</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="s">""</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">e</span> <span class="k">=&gt;</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="o">),</span>
      <span class="s">"four"</span> <span class="o">-&gt;</span> <span class="nc">SHtml</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">text</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="s">""</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">e</span> <span class="k">=&gt;</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="o">)</span> <span class="o">%</span> <span class="o">(</span><span class="s">"id"</span> <span class="o">-&gt;</span> <span class="s">"four_id"</span><span class="o">),</span>
      <span class="s">"five"</span> <span class="o">-%&gt;</span> <span class="nc">SHtml</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">text</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="s">""</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">e</span> <span class="k">=&gt;</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="o">)</span> <span class="o">%</span> <span class="o">(</span><span class="s">"id"</span> <span class="o">-&gt;</span> <span class="s">"five_id"</span><span class="o">)</span> <span class="o">%</span> <span class="o">(</span><span class="s">"maxlength"</span> <span class="o">-&gt;</span> <span class="s">"20"</span><span class="o">)</span>
    <span class="o">)</span>
  <span class="o">}</span>
<span class="o">}</span>
</pre>
<h3>+</h3>
<pre class="highlight html"><span class="nt">&lt;lift:Sample</span><span class="err">.</span><span class="na">sample</span> <span class="na">form=</span><span class="s">"POST"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;f:one/&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;f:two</span> <span class="na">id=</span><span class="s">"two_id"</span> <span class="nt">/&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;f:three</span> <span class="na">id=</span><span class="s">"three_id"</span> <span class="nt">/&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;f:four/&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;f:five</span> <span class="na">id=</span><span class="s">"other_id"</span><span class="nt">/&gt;</span>
<span class="err">&lt;</span>/lift:Sample.sample&gt;
</pre>
<h3>=</h3>
<pre class="highlight html"><span class="nt">&lt;form</span> <span class="na">action=</span><span class="s">"/sample"</span> <span class="na">method=</span><span class="s">"post"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;input</span> <span class="na">name=</span><span class="s">"F381921387278KLY"</span> <span class="na">value=</span><span class="s">""</span> <span class="na">type=</span><span class="s">"text"</span> <span class="nt">/&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;input</span> <span class="na">name=</span><span class="s">"F381921387279KPG"</span> <span class="na">value=</span><span class="s">""</span> <span class="na">type=</span><span class="s">"text"</span> <span class="nt">/&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;input</span> <span class="na">name=</span><span class="s">"F381921387280FIB"</span> <span class="na">value=</span><span class="s">""</span> <span class="na">type=</span><span class="s">"text"</span> <span class="na">id=</span><span class="s">"three_id"</span> <span class="nt">/&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;input</span> <span class="na">name=</span><span class="s">"F381921387281GUG"</span> <span class="na">value=</span><span class="s">""</span> <span class="na">type=</span><span class="s">"text"</span> <span class="na">id=</span><span class="s">"four_id"</span> <span class="nt">/&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;input</span> <span class="na">name=</span><span class="s">"F381921387282LYP"</span> <span class="na">value=</span><span class="s">""</span> <span class="na">type=</span><span class="s">"text"</span> <span class="na">id=</span><span class="s">"other_id"</span> <span class="na">maxlength=</span><span class="s">"20"</span> <span class="nt">/&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/form&gt;</span>
</pre>
<ul>
<li><strong>one</strong> - The most basic tag, there are no attributes in code nor markup.</li>
<li><strong>two</strong> - Same as above but with id attribute set in markup. As you can see in generated html this attribute is lost.</li>
<li><strong>three</strong> - <code>-%&gt;</code> syntax preserves markup attributes.</li>
<li><strong>four</strong> - Other way of setting html attributes.</li>
<li><strong>five</strong> - When setting attributes in both code and markup the second one has higher priority.</li>
</ul>
